{"tid":2427383,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"習近平：以實際行動和優異成績慶祝建黨100周年","createTime":"2021-02-28T18:16:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T15:00:49.000Z","uid":278587,"like":5,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"49bd695f83494733ffa2ac7a3caba9ef8f50b185","tid":2427383,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:16:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425638\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425638&d=FWesCxf%2Fx1R8NKF8yEGh3RPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=b414a85e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D425638&h=d35669b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=425638</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】今年是中國共產黨成立100周年，中共中央總書記習近平表示，要以實際行動和優異成績慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n中央政治局委員、書記處書記、全國人大常委會、國務院、全國政協黨組成員、最高人民法院、最高人民檢察院黨組書記，按規定向黨中央和習近平書面述職。習近平認真審閱述職報告，並提出重要要求。<br />\n<br />\n他強調，今年是中國共產黨成立100周年，亦是「十四五」開局之年，要更加緊密團結在黨中央周圍，切實把黨中央決策部署貫徹落實到各地區、各部門，各方面工作中以實際行動和優異成績慶祝建黨100周年。"},{"pid":"ed49d9a00661debd2e38adbc8d36c7a2de6ab23f","tid":2427383,"uid":197745,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T18:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b937aee5b0fd17be0c96ebd1672b961cc175e71c","tid":2427383,"uid":224066,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T22:06:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vXzn55c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvXzn55c.jpg&h=6c5d1725&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33b29d8520273aa0f8b1d5aa7acbddd9ba874591","tid":2427383,"uid":24730,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T22:17:02.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">九十九年成大錯 稱王只合在秦州</span></span>"},{"pid":"63ed1d30c39de4dc11530ad3fd87fdebf5f318